headline: MetLife: Decreasing Interest Rates Make Fixed Rate Preferred Stock Very Attractive

headline: MetLife and Global Citizen Announce Major Partnership to Drive Economic Change and Foster Resilient Communities
summary: NEW YORK, September 28, 2025--Today at the 2025 Global Citizen Festival, MetLife, a leading financial services company providing insurance and employee benefits, proudly announced becoming a major partner with Global Citizen, the world’s largest movement to end extreme poverty, with a new three-year partnership.
